# Linkedin Watcher Repository Structure

```
linkedin-watcher/
├── .cursor/                       # Cursor IDE configuration
├── config/                        # Configuration management
├── db/                            # Database layer
│   └── migrations/                # Database migration files
├── docs/                          # API documentation
├── infra/                         # Infrastructure components
├── internal/                      # Internal application code
│   ├── controllers/               # HTTP request handlers
│   ├── middleware/                # HTTP middleware
│   ├── models/                    # Domain models (API, business logic)
│   ├── routers/                   # HTTP routing
│   └── services/                  # Business logic/services
├── main.go                        # Application entry point
├── go.mod                         # Go module dependencies
├── Dockerfile                     # Production Docker configuration
├── docker-compose-dev.yml         # Development Docker Compose
├── docker-compose-prod.yml        # Production Docker Compose
└── sqlc.yaml                      # SQL code generation configuration
```

### Important: whenever a folder is created or removed, edit it here.
